{"tid":2167651,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有國才有家 - 古德明","createTime":"2020-08-21T08:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T09:07:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3a3c09d413de7664edd9357a0b9952083b9b0798","tid":2167651,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:50:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200821/MG5CADZCGVFTTBP5REGFE6INQA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200821%2FMG5CADZCGVFTTBP5REGFE6INQA%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=3bb65709\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200821%2FMG5CADZCGVFTTBP5REGFE6INQA%2F&h=48bc27f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200821/MG5CADZCGVFTTBP5REGFE6INQA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n有國才有家 - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QZaUCnyUY_Q0L3gY7F2ZLPF0kpo=/3844x2753/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7OPQA2M3JFHJLL3IFJDUS7DVUY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQZaUCnyUY_Q0L3gY7F2ZLPF0kpo%3D%2F3844x2753%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7OPQA2M3JFHJLL3IFJDUS7DVUY.jpg&h=ef653ec5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n七月三十日，鄭月娥政府發表聲明，支持選舉主任之禁民主派代表競逐立法會議席：「參選人必須效忠香港特別行政區；如欲當選之後，藉議員否決議案之權，迫使政府接受若干政治要求，即不符參選資格。」鄭月娥政府原來等於香港，對之不唯命是從即等於對港不忠。<br />\n<br />\n一九一五年，袁世凱計劃稱帝，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n今天可不同了：立法會議員受命於民者，只要是反對鄭月娥政府，就是「不效忠香港特別行政區」，就不得做議員。然則梁啟超、蔡鍔等，或用文章，或恃武力，「迫使政府接受若干政治要求」，無疑要問賣國叛國之罪，判處最少十年監禁。請不要說有民始有國，有國始有君；現在是有君始有國，有國始有民，有民始有家。<br />\n<br />\n而根據新香港的效忠論，秦檜完全聽從宋高宗命令，應是歷朝最會「效忠中國」的宰相。怪不得鄭月娥政府要大舉整頓歷史科教育。"},{"pid":"115c8387e89c7cb17d7a59b82278c0fb1b0f830f","tid":2167651,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T09:07:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">從小就學&quot;保家衛國&quot;，根據蚑共&quot;一國兩制&quot;解讀邏輯，保家定衛國先<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？？？</span></span></span></strong>"}]}